=== Probe A · ck_guest_rate_bucket_count_le_1 CHECK constraint ===
SQL: INSERT INTO guest_rate_bucket(id,device_fp,ip_hash,bucket_date,count)
       VALUES (999,'fp-x','ip-x','2026-05-17',2);
EXPECT: rejected (count > 1 violates biz §4.10 末尾 "上限 1/day")
ACTUAL: ERROR:  new row for relation "guest_rate_bucket" violates check
                constraint "ck_guest_rate_bucket_count_le_1"
        DETAIL: Failing row contains (999, fp-x, ip-x, 2026-05-17, 2, ...).
VERDICT: PASS — constraint fires correctly.

=== Probe B · uq_guest_rate_bucket_fp_ip_date 三元唯一索引 ===
SQL: INSERT INTO guest_rate_bucket VALUES (1001,'fp-1','ip-1','2026-05-17',1);  -- OK
     INSERT INTO guest_rate_bucket VALUES (1002,'fp-1','ip-1','2026-05-17',0);  -- expect dup
EXPECT: 1st insert ok, 2nd rejected (device_fp+ip_hash+bucket_date 三元唯一)
ACTUAL: INSERT 0 1
        ERROR:  duplicate key value violates unique constraint
                "uq_guest_rate_bucket_fp_ip_date"
        DETAIL: Key (device_fp, ip_hash, bucket_date)=(fp-1, ip-1, 2026-05-17) already exists.
VERDICT: PASS — biz §4.10 末尾 "(device_fp, ip_hash, date) 联合唯一" enforced.

=== Probe C · share_token.jti UNIQUE ===
SQL: INSERT INTO share_token VALUES (2001,'jti-aaa',7,'QUESTION','question:1',...);
     INSERT INTO share_token VALUES (2002,'jti-aaa',8,'EXAM_DAY','event:1',...);
EXPECT: 1st ok, 2nd rejected
ACTUAL: INSERT 0 1
        ERROR:  duplicate key value violates unique constraint "share_token_jti_key"
        DETAIL: Key (jti)=(jti-aaa) already exists.
VERDICT: PASS — biz §4.11 "jti VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL UNIQUE" enforced.

=== Probe D · uq_account_device (student_id, device_fp) 联合唯一 ===
